reviewText:
I did recieve it... the was the one star rating... the rest is a no star rating...it does not play.  It says wrong region.  So I guess if I ever go to another country I'll get to see it.
I did not contact the seller for a return.
Unfortunately this DVD was unable to be played

Nothing in the description lead me to know that the DVD would not play in a USA machine.  I was very disappointed that I did not get to keep my movie, however, seller did take the movie back without hesitation.  Good job seller, now I hope it's available from this seller in my Region 1, I would purchase from this seller again.
